{
  "_comment": [
    "IAM permissions policy for role agrisync-snapshot-prod (v2 HYBRID — Option δ 2026-05-17).",
    "spec: voice-diary-e2e-2026-05-17 (snapshot prereqs v2)",
    "runbook: _COFOUNDER/runbooks/prod-snapshot.md §1+§3+§5 (HYBRID DESIGN-APPROVED v2)",
    "",
    "Scope (founder lock v2):",
    "  WRITE-only to agrisync-snapshots-prod bucket (PutObject + GetObject for verify; NO Delete)",
    "  READ-only inventory on shramsafal-uploads-prod (List + GetObjectVersions)",
    "  READ-only inventory on shramsafal-voice-retained-prod (List + GetObjectVersions)",
    "  Encrypt + Decrypt + GenerateDataKey on alias/agrisync-snapshots-prod",
    "  CreateDBSnapshot + DescribeDBSnapshots + AddTagsToResource on shramsafal-prod-db (v2 HYBRID)",
    "",
    "v1 had GetSecretValue on agrisync/snapshot/pg-prod for pg_dump auth.",
    "v2 dropped that grant — RDS native snapshot is API-only, no DB credentials needed.",
    "(The secret entry itself is preserved in Secrets Manager as audit history but is",
    "no longer accessible by this role.)",
    "",
    "Notably: NO s3:DeleteObject / s3:DeleteObjectVersion anywhere. Combined with bucket",
    "versioning, this enforces append-only on the verification log AND the snapshot files",
    "themselves — only the bucket lifecycle policy (a bucket-owner action) can age them out.",
    "",
    "rds:DescribeDBSnapshots cannot be ARN-scoped (AWS limitation on list-type API).",
    "rds:CreateDBSnapshot scoped to both the DB instance ARN and the snapshot ARN pattern;",
    "AWS requires both for CreateDBSnapshot to authorize the action."
  ],
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "SnapshotBucketWriteAndReadForVerify",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:PutObject",
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:GetObjectVersion",
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListBucketVersions",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:s3:::agrisync-snapshots-prod",
        "arn:aws:s3:::agrisync-snapshots-prod/*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RawBlobInventoryReadOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListBucketVersions",
        "s3:GetBucketVersioning",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::shramsafal-uploads-prod"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RetainedVoiceInventoryReadOnly",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket",
        "s3:ListBucketVersions",
        "s3:GetBucketVersioning",
        "s3:GetBucketLocation"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::shramsafal-voice-retained-prod"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "KmsForSnapshotKey",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "kms:Encrypt",
        "kms:Decrypt",
        "kms:GenerateDataKey",
        "kms:DescribeKey"
      ],
      "Resource": "*",
      "Condition": {
        "ForAnyValue:StringEquals": {
          "kms:ResourceAliases": "alias/agrisync-snapshots-prod"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RdsCreateSnapshot",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "rds:CreateDBSnapshot",
      "Resource": [
        "arn:aws:rds:ap-south-1:951921970996:db:shramsafal-prod-db",
        "arn:aws:rds:ap-south-1:951921970996:snapshot:*"
      ]
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RdsDescribeSnapshots",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "rds:DescribeDBSnapshots",
      "Resource": "*"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "RdsTagSnapshot",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "rds:AddTagsToResource",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:rds:ap-south-1:951921970996:snapshot:*"
    }
  ]
}
